# SQL Schema

## User Table
- user_id (PK)
- name
- email
- password
- phone

## Translation Table
- translation_id (PK)
- user_id (FK)
- input_type
- input_content
- output_type
- output_content
- translation_date

## Dataset Table
- dataset_id (PK)
- language
- gesture_name
- category
- video_path

## History Table
- history_id (PK)
- translation_id (FK)
- result_type
- timestamp

## Admin Table
- admin_id (PK)
- name
- email
- password

## Report Table
- report_id (PK)
- admin_id (FK)
- report_type
- report_date
